metadata.name: Three Wise Monkeys of the 21st Century
metadata.description:
Three Wise Monkeys of 21st century - "see no evil, hear no evil, speak no evil"

The new representation of three wise monkeys in one:

Mizaru, who sees no evil, covering its eyes Kikazaru, who hears no evil, covering its ears, Iwazaru, who speaks no evil, covering its mouth.
